@page "/"

<PageTitle>BookStore - Splatt</PageTitle>

<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">📚 Welcome to BookStore</h1>
    <p class="lead">you can review your favorite books!</p>

    <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">✨ Features</h5>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                <li>🌍 <strong>Multi-language support:</strong> English, German, Spanish</li>
                                <li>🎲 <strong>Seed-based generation:</strong> Reproducible results</li>
                                <li>📊 <strong>Configurable likes & reviews:</strong> Fractional values supported</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                <li>♾️ <strong>Infinite scrolling:</strong> Load books on demand</li>
                                <li>🖼️ <strong>Multiple view modes:</strong> Table and Gallery views</li>
                                <li>📥 <strong>CSV Export:</strong> Export generated data</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-4">
        <a href="/books" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
            🚀 Start Generating Books
        </a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-10">
            <div class="card bg-light">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h6 class="card-title">📝 How it works:</h6>
                    <ol class="text-start">
                        <li><strong>Select a language/region</strong> - Choose from English (US), German (Germany), or Japanese (Japan)</li>
                        <li><strong>Configure the seed</strong> - Use the same seed to get identical results across sessions</li>
                        <li><strong>Set likes and reviews</strong> - Use sliders to control the average number of likes and reviews per book</li>
                        <li><strong>Browse the generated books</strong> - Scroll through an infinite list of realistic book data</li>
                        <li><strong>View book details</strong> - Click on any book to see cover image, reviews, and additional information</li>
                        <li><strong>Export your data</strong> - Download the currently loaded books as a CSV file</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
